      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>ketchup</strong> and the <strong>remaining jerk paste </strong>in a clean large bowl with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>jerk</strong> <strong>glaze</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
